cf46495d","address_line":"14 Einstein, Thủ Đức, Hồ Chí Minh 700000, Vietnam","category_ids":["bddb1c9e-9a56-4f6c-a1e6-6adb512dc1be","bf3ff727-ecb1-4ee9-900c-c3522f63ba6f","608ee8c3-6509-49a6-9d25-fe22af47ecf5","61c69526-79ef-4374-bd33-5166b60180e3"],"phone_number":"+84 968 100 100","review_count":3335,"opening_hours":null,"menu_image_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236193/mynook/venues/images/qlesyxdbscmrhofpwcxr.jpg","source_place_id":"0x317527a6e47c21bf:0xaac4c2c7eebbb865","duplicate_reason":"same_source_place_id","matched_venue_id":null,"selected_reviews":[{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236196/mynook/venues/images/ixdc64kdprveyaaoannq.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236196/mynook/venues/images/fbujxfpr9do0bfu2rjia.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236196/mynook/venues/images/bdqcorqw5q9kgqnloq6d.jpg"],"rating":3,"content":"Đến NH Sesan bao nhiêu lần cũng vậy phục vụ rất tốt 👍 k hề thiếu sót . Giá cả hợp lí .\\nNhưng mấy món hôm nay k vừa ý lắm . Món cơm chiên là món phổ biến nhưng Sesan xem thường nên k chăm chút , k ngon .\\nSalat nga thì sốt mayonnaise quá nhiều gây ngán .\\nẾch chiên bơ lại đi xào hành tây trộn vô làm ếch k giòn\\nRất mong Sesan chăm chút vào món ăn hơn . Sẽ quay lại .","author_name":"Ngoc Truong","published_at":"2 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xsaExXNUVVa3QyYURKMFNGQjJjMFpIVUVFeGNtYxAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236199/mynook/venues/images/zf6orojctvoqgftfczbi.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236199/mynook/venues/images/dvxgv2fsktwlbqiprug9.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236201/mynook/venues/images/ywhacycsuzyifrs315rc.jpg"],"rating":4,"content":"We were invited to having dinner with friends at this restaurant. The surounding of this restaurant is the best one I have been in here in HCMC so far.\\nThe food that came on the table is good, not wow as I would expected of a place like this. The staff was nice and observant.\\nSince we were a guest, not sure of the price point. But based on the surounding, it should be a more expensive place to have dinner.\\n\\nWould I be back to this restaurant, sure I would. Based on the food, surounding and staff as a total package.","author_name":"Ida Jørgensen","published_at":"5 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tka2JXcEhhMWxtY1RadmJqZGFSR3RtY1U1RFpWRRAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236206/mynook/venues/images/p5zmvsa1a2j8bmvsdqfe.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236204/mynook/venues/images/uju2ggwyhq0o5jscmujc.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236204/mynook/venues/images/sqjwpvlfqer99gtedgdh.jpg"],"rating":5,"content":"Nhà hàng có thực phẩm (hải sản) tươi sống hàng tuyển phong phú và chế biến ngon.\\nKhông gian rộng rãi, lịch sự, đẹp và sang.\\nNhân viên phục vụ chuyên nghiệp.","author_name":"Giang Nguyen","published_at":"4 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xkclpVNTFUV2hXZGxCd2QybGljSFIzWDA1d2VYYxAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236211/mynook/venues/images/nlgdf0spgiuxshentsyj.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236209/mynook/venues/images/miawbkizaqbagh770f2k.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236209/mynook/venues/images/a3otvegemiuziojndrkb.jpg"],"rating":4,"content":"Đồ ăn 6-7 điểm tuỳ món.\\nKhông gian quán bên ngoài decor đẹp, phù hợp tiếp khách. Không gian phòng bên trong thì bình thường, giống không gian ăn cưới.","author_name":"Thunga Nguyen","published_at":"5 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21walpEaFJUR1JJVDFFdFJHMVZYM05vUkZoR0xVRRAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236214/mynook/venues/images/ve9twm6t5hmdqthtgxng.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236214/mynook/venues/images/gauisntdtz9cmkekwaub.jpg"],"rating":5,"content":"Không gian rộng rãi, đa dạng các phòng VIP, đồ ăn chế biến ngon, giá thì hơi cao so với mặt bằng chung khu vực, tuy nhiên cũng hợp lý do phân khúc cao cấp hơn. Đã tới đây vài lần.\\nNơi hợp lý nếu cần tiếp đón cần không gian riêng tư.","author_name":"Truong Nguyen","published_at":"4 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT200NFZrWmlVM05IZDBoZlZYbzJSamhoVDJsTFFYYxAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236217/mynook/venues/images/woynha6sa3nd9n4nqxdn.jpg"],"rating":5,"content":"- Khoa mình đã tổ chức tiệc Tất niên ở đây, dịch vụ và đồ ăn khá ổn.\\n- Về không gian thì không phải bàn cãi, quá chuẩn chỉnh và sang trọng.","author_name":"Tuấn Nguyễn","published_at":"3 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aUVowMUxia00wWjB3M2FTMVpOa2RUUlZack1HYxAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236221/mynook/venues/images/kqiu5qvgrhhtctpkw9vb.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236222/mynook/venues/images/j7zevsswmurcf9di6tkz.jpg","https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236222/mynook/venues/images/tquqglmmdscqonjvs9ob.jpg"],"rating":4,"content":"Nhà hàng khá lớn với không gian thoáng cà rộng. Menu đa dạng, tuy nhiên chế biến cũng tùy món ngon có dở quá. Nhân viên đông, care khách chu đáo.","author_name":"Brian Nguyen","published_at":"6 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xjeFFWaExTekJUVmxkNlFWbERWbE55TldaTlpuYxAB"},{"media":["https://res.cloudinary.com/dqksxhlxn/image/upload/v1778236224/mynook/venues/images/rymfvcmfymbmm0jttswv.jpg"],"rating":5,"content":"Đồ ăn rất ngon nhaa, dịch vụ rất rất chu đáo, nên thử nha mn","author_name":"Hoang Minh","published_at":"3 months ago","source_review_id":"Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4b2FuTjJNelJPWlZOUFVEVXhiVzR4ZVdSRU5uYxAB"}],"primary_category_id":"bddb1c9e-9a56-4f6c-a1e6-6adb512dc1be"}'[31m,
